high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table on the right.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table on the left of the metal plate.
Turn right and go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and go to the toaster on the right side of the stove. .
Place the knife on the right side of the toaster.
Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up one slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on the left.
Chill the lettuce in the refrigerator before taking it out.
Turn left and go to the counter with the toaster on the right.
Place the lettuce in the front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Go to the table on your left.
Pick up the knife near the left edge of the table.
Go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Set the knife down on the counter to the right of the toaster.
Turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up a piece of lettuce.
Go past the stove on the left to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Move to the counter on the left.
Set the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn right and walk forward to face the toaster on the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn right and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Step left to face the counter.
Place the lettuce slice on the counter to the left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To cool a lettuce slice plus place it on the counter by the fridge.
